ERR_PNPM_FROZEN_LOCKFILE_CHANGED  The lockfile is out of sync with the package.json file.

According to "pnpm-lock.yaml", the following dependencies should have been hoisted to <root>:
  - name: "pkg.json"
    version: "1.0.0"

But they are not.

Run "pnpm install" to update the lockfile.

Hint: if you want to update the lockfile, you can run "pnpm update --lockfile"
